    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
